    "Name": "Longbow",
    "Details": "The -10C is a refresh of the -8C, converting it to use more advanced technology. By changing to double heat sinks, 8 tons of cooling can be dropped while still improving the performance. The freed tons are used to add Artemis IV capabilities to all the LRM launchers, replacing the lasers with their extended range counterpart and adding CASE protection to the side torso. Another ton of ammo was also added, while keeping the same level of armoring.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Anti-Air Targeting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.15</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
